snippet: The New Orleans Jazz Orchestra celebrated its anniversary with a guest-laden concert at Carnegie Hall, which was broadcast back home, on Monday.
abstract: Nate Chinen reviews performance by the New Orleans Jazz Orchestra and guests at Carnegie Hall.
